eck inbox first \u2014 handle messages before starting new work\\n- Pick highest-priority open task assigned to you\\n- Work on it until complete or blocked\\n- Mark tasks done via API when finished\\n- Write status updates to status.md\\n\\n## Communication\\n\\n- DM teammates via their chat_inbox/ folder\\n- Post team updates to public/team_channel/\\n- Escalate blockers to alice or the CEO\\n\\n## Quality\\n\\n- Code must be runnable (test before marking done)\\n- Feature code goes in backend/, strategies/, lib/ \u2014 not agent output/\\n- Every task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API \u2014 see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_01_21_31_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"FOUNDER PRIORITY: We are building the Kalshi Alpha Dashboard together. This is our core product delivery goal.\\n\\nSPEC: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md (READ THIS)\\n\\nASSIGNMENTS:\\n- Bob: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js (Express on port 3200, 5 endpoints)\\n- Dave: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/index.html (single-page frontend)\\n- Grace: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh (pipeline scheduler)\\n- Liam: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/monitor.js (monitoring alerts)\\n- Alice: Coordinate all, verify integration\\n\\nTrading pipeline is at: agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js\\nTrade signals output: agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json\\n\\nDONE = node agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js starts AND index.html shows live signals in browser.\\n\\nEveryone: check your assigned task on the task board. Start building NOW. Coordinate via status.md. This is P0.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update \u2014 Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). \u2014 Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation \u2014 Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) \u2014 the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"running\"}]}\n./logs/cycles/0020_RESUME_2026_04_03_11_31_03_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"judy\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# Normal Mode SOP\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nNormal mode is the default operating mode. Agents work at a steady pace on assigned tasks.\\n\\n## Priorities\\n\\n1. Complete assigned tasks\\n2. Claim unassigned tasks that match your skills\\n3. Create new tasks if you identify gaps\\n4. Coordinate with teammates via chat_inbox\\n5. Report progress to Alice (Lead Coordinator)\\n\\n## Work Cycle\\n\\n- Check inbox first \u2014 handle messages before starting new work\\n- Pick highest-priority open task assigned to you\\n- Work on it until complete or blocked\\n- Mark tasks done via API when finished\\n- Write status updates to status.md\\n\\n## Communication\\n\\n- DM teammates via their chat_inbox/ folder\\n- Post team updates to public/team_channel/\\n- Escalate blockers to alice or the CEO\\n\\n## Quality\\n\\n- Code must be runnable (test before marking done)\\n- Feature code goes in backend/, strategies/, lib/ \u2014 not agent output/\\n- Every task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\\n## Knowledge Sharing \u2014 Culture & Consensus\\n\\nThe team maintains a shared knowledge base at `public/consensus.md`. **You should read it every fresh session** (it appears in your context under \\\"Team Culture & Consensus\\\").\\n\\n**When to WRITE a culture entry:**\\n- You discover a decision that affects the whole team (strategy change, security requirement, architecture choice)\\n- You learn something that would prevent a teammate from making a mistake\\n- You complete a significant task and want to record the outcome as a norm\\n\\n**How to post:**\\n```bash\\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/consensus/entry \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"type\\\":\\\"culture\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"What you learned\\\",\\\"section\\\":\\\"Category\\\"}'\\n```\\nTypes: `culture` (norms/learnings), `decision` (explicit choices), `group` (team agreements), `authority` (who owns what)\\n\\n**Also use your `knowledge/` folder** for agent-specific notes you want to persist across sessions:\\n- Write important findings to `agents/{your-name}/knowledge/{topic}.md`\\n- Read it at the start of fresh sessions when tackling that topic again\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API \u2014 see /api/consensus)*\\n| 1 | culture | Paper trading mode is required before any live order submission. Use PAPER_TRADING env flag. Never submit real orders without explicit founder approval. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 2 | culture | mean_reversion is our primary strategy (85.7% win rate in backtests). momentum and crypto_edge are disabled \u2014 10-11% win rates. Do not re-enable without data. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 3 | culture | All API endpoints must require auth via Authorization header. No open POST endpoints in production. Pattern: check Bearer token before processing. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 4 | culture | Confidence threshold is 0.80 minimum for signal execution. Signals below 80% confidence are filtered by SignalEngine. Do not lower this threshold without backtesting. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 5 | decision | Kalshi is our primary trading venue. All trading infrastructure targets the Kalshi prediction market API. Task 236 blocks live API until credentials obtained from kalshi.com. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 6 | group | When you learn something important about strategy, security, or architecture \u2014 post a culture entry via: curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/consensus/entry -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" -d \\\"{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"culture\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"...\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"section\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"...\\\\\\\"}\\\" | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":3,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_01_21_31_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"FOUNDER PRIORITY: We are building the Kalshi Alpha Dashboard together. This is our core product delivery goal.\\n\\nSPEC: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md (READ THIS)\\n\\nASSIGNMENTS:\\n- Bob: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js (Express on port 3200, 5 endpoints)\\n- Dave: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/index.html (single-page frontend)\\n- Grace: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh (pipeline scheduler)\\n- Liam: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/monitor.js (monitoring alerts)\\n- Alice: Coordinate all, verify integration\\n\\nTrading pipeline is at: agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js\\nTrade signals output: agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json\\n\\nDONE = node agents/